---

<Layout
    title="Mirating From SAP To ERPNext For Our Client: A Success Story! | Sanskar Technolab"
    ,
    description="Skilled ERPNext developers at Sanskar Technolab helped our client in saving $1166% with seamless SAP to ERPNext migration and end-to-end ERPNext implementation."
    ,
    keyword="erp implementation partner, erpnext implementation, erp implementation partner, erp implementation companies, ERPNext software development company, ERPNext development services, Erpnext solution company, Frappe ERPNext, Erpnext software, ERPNext open-source, ServiceNow company, Servicenow implementation services"
    ,
    description="Sanskar Technolab is your trusted partner to avail best ERPNext implementation services from the best minds."
    ,
    canonical_href="https://sanskartechnolab.com/sap_to_erpnext_migration"
>
    <!-- Banner Section -->
    <section
        class="hidden lg:flex section-bg h-[110vh] xl:h-[100vh] 2xl:h-[75vh] flex items-center banner-bg"
    >
        <div
            class="flex flex-wrap items-center mx-5 md:max-w-7xl md:mx-auto md:px-24 2xl:px-0"
        >
            <div class="w-full md:w-6/12">
                <h1
                    class="mr-10 text-[1.75rem] md:text-[3rem] !leading-tight xl:!leading-snug md:leading-[3.5rem] text-[#31393C] font-semibold"
                >
                Mirating From SAP To ERPNext For Our Client: A Success Story!
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="mr-20 text[#31393C] text-base md:text-lg !leading-7 md:leading-6 mt-5"
                >
                    Sanskar Technolab is the leading ERPNext partner, providing
                    a diverse range of services to our clients. This time, we
                    have provided end-to-end and seamless SAP to ERPNext
                    migration services.
                </p>
                <div
                    class="mt-7 flex justify-between bg-[#3E96F4] rounded-lg px-3 md:px-3 lg:px-5 py-2 md:py-2 lg:py-3 md:w-72 sm:w-auto"
                >
                    <a
                        href="/contact-us"
                        class="text-white text-base font-semibold font-inter"
                        >Schedule a Free demo now</a
                    >
                    <Image
                        loading="eager"
                        src={right}
                        width={6}
                        height={12}
                        alt="right arrow"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>

            <Image
                loading="eager"
                src={banner_image}
                alt="banner_sap_to_erpnext_migration"
                class="md:w-6/12 pl-10 2xl:ml-auto"
            />
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-bg flex items-center md:flex lg:hidden banner-bg">
        <div
            class="flex flex-wrap items-center mx-5 gap-5 md:max-w-7xl md:mx-auto md:px-24 2xl:px-0"
        >
            <div class="w-full lg:w-6/12 mt-5">
                <div
                    class="text-[1.75rem] md:text-[3rem] leading-9 md:leading-[3.5rem] text-[#31393C] font-semibold"
                >
                Mirating From SAP To ERPNext For Our Client: A Success Story!
                </div>
                <p
                    class="text[#31393C] text-sm md:text-base !leading-5 md:leading-6 mt-5"
                >
                    Sanskar Technolab is the leading ERPNext partner, providing
                    a diverse range of services to our clients. This time, we
                    have provided end-to-end and seamless SAP to ERPNext
                    migration services.
                </p>
                <div
                    class="mt-4 md:mt-7 flex justify-between bg-[#3E96F4] rounded-lg px-3 md:px-3 lg:px-5 py-2 md:py-2 lg:py-3 md:w-72 sm:w-auto"
                >
                    <a
                        href="/contact-us"
                        class="text-white text-base font-semibold font-inter"
                        >Schedule a Free demo now
                    </a>
                    <Image
                        loading="eager"
                        src={right}
                        width={6}
                        height={12}
                        alt="right arrow"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>

            <Image
                loading="eager"
                src={banner_image}
                alt="banner_sap_to_erpnext_migration"
                class="mx-auto mb-10"
            />
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Subtle Glimpses of the Project. -->
    <section
        class="py-[2rem] md:py-[2rem] lg:pb-[4rem] lg:pt-[6rem] mt-0 sm:mt-48 md:mt-0 lg:mt-0 xl:mt-0"
    >
        <div class="mx-5 md:max-w-7xl md:mx-auto md:px-24 2xl:px-0">
            <h2
                class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold text-[#3E96F4] leading-[2.25rem] md:leading-[2.75rem] lg:leading-[3rem]"
            >
                Subtle Glimpses of the Project.
            </h2>
            <div
                class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-0 md:gap-10 lg:gap-14 xl:gap-20 mt-4 md:mt-8 lg:mt-8"
            >
                <div
                    class="md:flex gap-6 md:gap-6 lg:gap-4 xl:gap-6 2xl:gap-10"
                >
                    <Image
                        loading="eager"
                        class="-ml-5 md:ml-0"
                        src={vijay_logo}
                        alt="Unique Approach"
                        width={205}
                        height={65}
                    />
                    <p
                        class="text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base text-[#31393C] font-normal leading-4 md:leading-5 lg:leading-6 my-auto"
                    >
                        Vijay Pure Natural Healthy Food is the leading
                        manufacturer of puffed rice(Murmura or Mamara) and
                        poha(pohay). This renowned B2B and B2C company is using
                        SAP to track and manage their business operations.
                        Considering its hefty costs and complex usage, they have
                        decided to switch from SAP to ERPNext by partnering with
                        Sanskar Technolab.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-10 lg:gap-10 xl:gap-20 mt-6 md:mt-0 lg:mt-0 ml-0 md:ml-5 lg:ml-0"
                >
                    <div>
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <p
                                class="text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base text-[#31393C] font-normal leading-4 md:leading-5 lg:leading-6"
                            >
                                <span
                                    class="text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4 md:leading-5 lg:leading-6 font-semibold"
                                    >Client Location
                                </span>
                                <br /> Ahmedabad, Gujarat.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p
                                class="text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base text-[#31393C] font-normal leading-4 md:leading-5 lg:leading-6"
                            >
                                <span
                                    class="text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4 md:leading-5 lg:leading-6 font-semibold"
                                    >Tech-Stack
                                </span>
                                <br /> Web Server: Frappe Cloud Database: MySQL (Maria
                                DB) ERPNext Version: 14.13.0
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <p
                                class="text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base text-[#31393C] font-normal leading-4 md:leading-5 lg:leading-6"
                            >
                                <span
                                    class="text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4 md:leading-5 lg:leading-6 font-semibold"
                                    >Industry
                                </span>
                                <br /> Construction
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p
                                class="text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base text-[#31393C] font-normal leading-4 md:leading-5 lg:leading-6"
                            >
                                <span
                                    class="text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4 md:leading-5 lg:leading-6 font-semibold"
                                    >Project Methodology
                                </span>
                                <br /> Agile Scrum Methodology
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What does the client want from us? -->
    <section class="py-[2rem] md:py-[2rem] lg:py-[4rem]">
        <div
            class="grid place-items-center grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-16 mx-5 md:max-w-7xl md:mx-auto md:px-24 2xl:px-0"
        >
            <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-center lg:justify-start">
                <Image
                    loading="eager"
                    src={section_client}
                    alt="What Does Client Want"
                    width={504}
                    height={417}
                />
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2
                    class="text-[#3E96F4] pb-2 md:pb-4 lg:pb-6 font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl leading-[1.75rem] md:leading-[2.25rem] lg:leading-[2.75rem]"
                >
                    What does the client want from us?
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="text-[#31393C] pb-2 md:pb-4 lg:pb-6 leading-4 md:leading-5 lg:leading-6 text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base font-normal"
                >
                    Vijay, the CEO of Vijay Pure Natural Healthy Food, wanted to
                    migrate to a simplistic platform with lesser maintenance and
                    support requirements. At the same time, they wanted the
                    migration process to be quick without disrupting their
                    day-to-day business operations. They also wanted us to keep
                    them informed throughout the project - for desired results.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Challenges of SAP & solutions with ERPNext for Vijay Pure Natural Healthy Food! -->
    <section class="section-bg-right">
        <div
            class="mx-5 md:max-w-7xl md:mx-auto md:px-24 2xl:px-0 py-[2rem] md:py-[2rem] lg:py-[4rem] text-center"
        >
            <div class="text-start md:text-center mb-5 md:mb-10 lg:mb-12">
                <h2
                    class="mx-0 md:mx-[0rem] lg:mx-[0rem] xl:mx-[10rem] text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl lg:!leading-[2.75rem] lg:text-[2.25rem] text-[#3E96F4] font-bold"
                >
                    Challenges of SAP & solutions with ERPNext for Vijay Pure
                    Natural Healthy Food!
                </h2>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 mt-0 sm:mt-10 md:mt-0 lg:mt-0 text-[#31393C] justify-items-center"> -->
            <div
                class="flex flex-wrap mt-0 sm:mt-10 md:mt-0 lg:mt-0 text-[#31393C] justify-items-center"
            >
                <!-- first card -->
                <div
                    class="lg:w-4/12 first_card w-full rounded-t-[10px] lg:rounded-tl-[10px] md:rounded-none"
                >
                    <div
                        class="pt-5 text-[#31393C] grid gap-2 font-semibold lg:text-base md:text-sm text-sm"
                    >
                        <p>SAP is super expensive…</p>
                        <p>Why?</p>
                        <p>HANA - Hardware cost</p>
                        <p>Annual License Fees</p>
                        <p>SAP Consultants + Niche Skills</p>
                    </div>
                    <Image
                        src={sap_challanging_bg}
                        alt="sap challanging bg"
                        class="w-full lg:mt-auto md:mt-[2rem] lg:rounded-l-[10px]"
                    />
                </div>

                <!-- second card -->
                <div
                    class="lg:w-4/12 md:w-6/12 w-full text-[#31393C] text-left"
                >
                    <p
                        class="bg-[#FFEFD5] lg:p-5 md:p-4 p-3 lg:text-xl md:text-[17px] flex items-center md:h-20 h-16 text-md font-semibold"
                    >
                        What are the challenges with the SAP ERP faced by our
                        client?
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="flex bg-[#FFFBF4] lg:p-5 md:p-4 p-3 md:h-20 h-16 items-center gap-2 border-t border-t-[#ADBDCD]"
                    >
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={high_hardware_cost}
                            alt="high_hardware_cost"
                        />
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4"
                        >
                            High hardware costs.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex bg-[#FFFBF4] lg:p-5 md:h-20 h-16 md:p-4 p-3 items-center gap-2 border-t border-t-[#ADBDCD]"
                    >
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={higher_per_user}
                            alt="higher_per_user"
                        />
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] text-xs my-2 md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4"
                        >
                            Higher per user onboarding charges.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex bg-[#FFFBF4] lg:p-5 md:h-20 h-16 md:p-4 p-3 items-center gap-2 border-t border-t-[#ADBDCD]"
                    >
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={annual_licensing}
                            alt="annual_licensing"
                            class="my-2"
                        />
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4"
                        >
                            Additional annual licensing charges.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex bg-[#FFFBF4] lg:p-5 md:h-20 h-16 md:p-4 p-3 items-center gap-2 border-t border-t-[#ADBDCD]"
                    >
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={complex_system}
                            alt="complex_system"
                            class="my-[2.5px]"
                        />
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4"
                        >
                            Complex system to deal with!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex bg-[#FFFBF4] lg:p-5 md:p-4 md:h-20 h-16 p-3 items-center gap-2 border-t border-t-[#ADBDCD]"
                    >
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={quite_difficult}
                            alt="quite_difficult"
                        />
                        <p
                            class="text-left text-[#31393C] text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4"
                        >
                            Quite difficult to customize to meet specific
                            business needs.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- third card -->
                <div
                    class="lg:w-4/12 md:w-6/12 w-full text-[#31393C] text-left"
                >
                    <p
                        class="bg-[#C8E2FF] lg:p-5 md:p-4 md:h-20 h-16 p-3 lg:rounded-tr-[10px] flex items-center lg:text-xl md:text-lg text-md font-semibold"
                    >
                        How ERPNext is the ideal ERP for their business?
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="flex bg-[#DFEFFF] lg:p-5 md:p-4 md:h-20 h-16 p-3 items-center gap-2 border-t border-t-[#ADBDCD]"
                    >
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={lower_upfront}
                            alt="lower_upfront"
                        />
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4"
                        >
                            Lower upfront costs.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex bg-[#DFEFFF] lg:p-5 md:p-4 md:h-20 h-16 p-3 items-center gap-2 border-t border-t-[#ADBDCD]"
                    >
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={free_user_onbording}
                            alt="free_user_onbording"
                        />
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] my-2 text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4"
                        >
                            Free user onboarding.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex bg-[#DFEFFF] lg:p-5 md:p-4 md:h-20 h-16 p-3 items-center gap-2 border-t border-t-[#ADBDCD]"
                    >
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={no_ongoing_licensing}
                            alt="no_ongoing_licensing"
                        />
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] text-xs text-left md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4"
                        >
                            No ongoing licensing fees due to its open-source
                            nature.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex bg-[#DFEFFF] lg:p-5 md:p-4 md:h-20 h-16 p-3 items-center gap-2 border-t border-t-[#ADBDCD]"
                    >
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={quite_easy}
                            alt="quite_easy"
                        />
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4"
                        >
                            Quite easy for both developers & end users!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex bg-[#DFEFFF] lg:!rounded-br-[10px] lg:rounded-none lg:p-5 md:p-4 md:h-20 h-16 p-3 items-center gap-2 border-t border-t-[#ADBDCD]"
                    >
                        <Image
                            loading="eager"
                            src={customization_system}
                            alt="customization_system"
                        />
                        <p
                            class="text-[#31393C] text-left text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base leading-4"
                        >
                            Easily customizable system and modules to meet
                            specific business needs.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Results -->
    <section
        class="py-[2rem] md:py-[2rem] lg:py-[4rem]"
    >
        <div class="mx-5 md:max-w-7xl md:mx-auto md:px-24 2xl:px-0">
            <h2
                class="text-left md:text-center text-[#3E96F4] font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl leading-[1.75rem] md:leading-[2.25rem] lg:leading-[2.75rem] pb-4 md:pb-4 lg:pb-6"
            >
                Our Results
            </h2>

            <Image
                loading="eager"
                class="flex flex-wrap justify-center mt-2 mx-auto"
                src={result_section}
                alt="Result"
                width={1100}
                height={259}
            />

            <div class="mx-auto mt-10">
                <div
                    class="md:flex flex-wrap text-[#31393C] mt-5 shadow-none gap-10 2xl:gap-16"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full lg:w-4/12 text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base text-[#31393C] mt-5 md:mt-5 lg:mt-0"
                    >
                        <p class="font-semibold">
                            The team at Sanskar Technolab thoroughly
                            understands their unique business needs and
                            migration process to ensure seamless and desired end
                            results for the clients.
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl mt-5 mb-2 font-semibold"
                        >
                            Here’s the key part:
                        </p>
